We are deeply indebted to dung
beetles.

00:12:21.250 --> 00:12:22.370
&gt;
 

00:12:22.370 --> 00:12:22.820
Believe me.
 

00:12:22.820 --> 00:12:25.080
And to fungi.
 

00:12:25.080 --> 00:12:28.470
What's going off here is
respiration.

00:12:28.470 --> 00:12:29.330
So that's energy.
 

00:12:29.330 --> 00:12:31.058
You know, you all use it up
every day.

00:12:31.058 --> 00:12:33.871
You're using up somewhere
between oh 3500 and 5000

00:12:33.871 --> 00:12:36.455
calories a day,
depending on whether you're on

00:12:36.455 --> 00:12:37.889
a sports team or not.
 

